'''Code 1-5''' was the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] order to begin evacuating [[Echo Base/Legends|Echo Base]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]]. It was used during the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]] when [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[All Terrain Armored Transport/Legends|AT-ATs]] overran the base's defenses.

The Rebels evacuated their equipment and personnel using [[GR-75 medium transport/Legends|Rebel transports]]. The [[Transport/Legends|transports]] attempted to breach the Imperial [[Blockade/Legends|blockade]] around the planet one-by-one along random escape vectors, supported by Echo Base's [[Ion cannon/Legends|ion cannon]] and a minimal escort of two [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] to each [[Starship/Legends|starship]].

